data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the charming Stonehill subdivision of Sherwood, AR! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence built in 2002 offers an exceptional blend of modern comfort and timeless elegance. Step inside and be captivated by the spacious and inviting interior. The heart of the home is the well-appointed eat-in kitchen, perfect for both casual meals and entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience firsthand the comfort, elegance, and charm that this home has to offer. Your new chapter begins here!
